snippet: The former Nascar driver Dick Trickle apparently died from a self-inflicted gunshot wound on Thursday.
abstract: Former Nascar driver Dick Trickle apparently dies from a self-inflicted gunshot wound; his body is found at a cemetery in Boger City, NC, about 40 miles northwest of Charlotte.
lead_paragraph: The former Nascar driver Dick Trickle apparently died from a self-inflicted gunshot wound on Thursday.

headline.seo: Former Nascar Driver Dick Trickle Dies
headline.main: Trickle, a Former Nascar Driver, Dies at 71
